{"tid":2443182,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"40歲張柏芝爆3胎生父成謎又懷孕 驚人巨肚現形","createTime":"2021-03-12T01:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T05:56:14.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8d9b383cb0b4b0e06e7362e4ec6291c84038ed92","tid":2443182,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:39:28.000Z","msg":"40歲港星張柏芝近日因為登上大陸節目《乘風破浪的姐姐2》讓她人氣再攀高峰，一舉一<br />\n動格外受到矚目。只是她2018年底突然宣布生下第3胎兒子Marcus，至今生父成謎，日前<br />\n又被網友直擊她挺著圓滾滾的大肚現身菜市場畫面，引發懷孕傳聞。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n張柏芝近日被網友直擊現身上海某菜市場買菜，過程中還不小心掉了幾張鈔票在地上，經<br />\n過路人2度提醒才反應過來，呆萌模樣被讚超可愛。但就有網友注意到張柏芝的肚子大到<br />\n連外套都遮不住，忍不住PO出截圖質疑：「張柏芝真的不是懷四胎了嗎？最新的菜市場買<br />\n菜照肚子很明顯啊，這也不是角度問題吧。」<br />\n <br />\n張柏芝近日上菜市場，驚人巨肚成亮點。(取自微博)<br />\n <br />\n張柏芝挺著巨肚的截圖，更在陸網引發熱烈討論，「太像懷孕」、「她第三個孩子爸爸是<br />\n誰我還沒搞明白」、「我的天哪這種程度得五個月了」、「這肯定是了吧，太明顯了」，<br />\n但也有人認為張柏芝生過3胎難免會有肚子，感嘆「她直播都說過沒有懷孕，為啥女明星<br />\n肚子胖一點就被說懷孕啊」。<br />\n <br />\n20140511中天新聞　三年懷孕五次？　張栢芝曝曾流產四次<br />\n <br />\n張柏芝2011年與謝霆鋒結束5年婚姻，獨力撫養2個兒子Lucas與Quintus。離奇的是，一直<br />\n維持單身的她，卻在2018年12月突然透過工作室宣布產下第3胎兒子Marcus，至今仍不願<br />\n鬆口孩子爸爸身分。曾有人從張柏芝所公開的照片找出蛛絲馬跡，發現Marcus頭髮呈淡金<br />\n色，還有網友忍不住直接留言詢問這問題，獲張柏芝親自回覆：「圈外的不可以嗎？」被<br />\n推測Marcus的生父可能是外國人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210311006058-260404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20210311006058-260404&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=ac32c1cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210311006058-260404</a>"},{"pid":"304caadc55c0dcd18e659ecf4b28f86c0a2a548a","tid":2443182,"uid":235637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"我屌大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52337ebed5033207eb28afe0243b30e84f381620","tid":2443182,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:41:28.000Z","msg":"Edison<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ec364dc409cb7ecbec1499b63a33ff30682ff5","tid":2443182,"uid":212168,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:42:16.000Z","msg":"真正肉便器"},{"pid":"d537995e45b14fb428555544ade5f1209568f846","tid":2443182,"uid":32588,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:43:56.000Z","msg":"鍾意扑嘢同生仔<br />\n就係唔鍾意男人"},{"pid":"44e9b3ffaca64847f033d83dcab0c23e7adb7287","tid":2443182,"uid":8410,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:44:26.000Z","msg":"呢條八婆， 人人都上得， 仲要生埋， 真係cheap"},{"pid":"5ebc5fff9165458ef25d2c48de594b343fed0b38","tid":2443182,"uid":20867,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:51:15.000Z","msg":"（臉容變成了「他」的形狀。。。）<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Untitled-14-8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FUntitled-14-8.jpg&h=c689593b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40a3144a3a4a119e72a3b25c10ee229777950623","tid":2443182,"uid":140599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:52:28.000Z","msg":"條女咁中意比人中出既"},{"pid":"418d73ae64762b6d81e0da766ade74c419e411be","tid":2443182,"uid":146621,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:03:52.000Z","msg":"淫還淫<br />\n點解唔戴套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044498ee101031b12f0ef07124468d241386d12c","tid":2443182,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ebc5fff9165458ef25d2c48de594b343fed0b38","tid":2443182,"uid":20867,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:51:15.000Z","msg":"（臉容變成了「他」的形狀。。。）<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Untitled-14-8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FUntitled-14-8.jpg&h=c689593b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20